fields.name: meanX
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF X coordinate

fields.name: meanY
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF Y coordinate

fields.name: meanZ
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF Z coordinate

fields.name: obs
fields.description: Number of position observations used during survey-in

fields.name: valid
fields.description: Survey-in position validity flag, 1 = valid, otherwise 0

fields.name: active
fields.description: Survey-in in progress flag, 1 = in-progress, otherwise 0

issues: Minor casing inconsistency: 'meanY' is capitalized while 'meanx', 'meanz', and 'meanv' are lowercase

adjudication.reasoning: The UBX-TIM-SVIN message is identical across u-blox 8 and F9 generations. All three extractions correctly identify the 28-byte payload structure and the data types of each field. The variations are purely stylistic or minor typographical differences in field naming (e.g., lowercase 'meanx' vs camelCase 'meanX' or 'reserved0' vs 'reserved1'). The fundamental protocol definition (Class 0x0D, ID 0x04, Length 28) is consistent across all sources.
